///                                                 * Decode tree-encoded key-frame B mode. Tree offset specified as arg3. The two-dimensional offset [10][10] is split into arg3[7:4] and arg3[3:0] fields.
///                                                 ###
///                                    : DEC_KF_UV_MODE            0x8
///                                                 ###
///                                                 * Decode tree-encoded key-frame UV mode.
///                                                 ###
