///                                                 * Decode tree-encoded non-key-frame B mode.
///                                                 ###
///                                    : DEC_UV_MODE               0xB
///                                                 ###
///                                                 * Decode tree-encoded non-key-frame UV mode.
///                                                 ###
///                                    : DEC_MV_REF                0xC
