/// $INTERFACE ClkRstBiu               biu              (4,4)
///     ###
///     * Common Biu Unit used for block level reset and clock gating control
///     ###
///     # # ----------------------------------------------------------
///     @ 0x00000 CRCtl                (P)
///               ###
///               * Clock Reset Control Register
///               ###
///               %unsigned 1  rst                       0x1
